On 12/14/04 12:41 AM, "tcs" <tcs1968(-at-)yahoo.com> wrote:

> My question is there a way to eliminate using the power brake servo, Maybe be
> using the earlier 68-70 master cylinder ?  Will this work with the front disc
> brakes?  

Before eliminating the power brake system, take a drive in another bus,
coast it with the clutch, put it in neutral, cut the engine and try to stop
it with the brakes. You'll be horrified how hard it is without the booster.

